Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It should be daybreak there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sea at daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Appreciating that is something a worthless student would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:06.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it is a disgusting winter sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Okajima-kun is in the Sea of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prepare two plane tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A business trip, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go there as well, to the Sea of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:55.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to suffer like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think a gun costs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They came here to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:17.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Department Chief causing me to go through this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have something mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:25.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They want to destroy that data disk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is just-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.81,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My life is just an accessory to that. Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's a torpedo in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:33.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this seem weird to you, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something's weird, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're not shooting at all now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They should be able to make us into swiss cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. Something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:56.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny-Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:01.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're 5,000 meters behind us and they're keeping that distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:13.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The water way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the water way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:24.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The path from here to Balawan is filled with rocks and mangroves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep going it's just going to get tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the end we won't even be able to take evasive maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:33.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that I suck at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to evade to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We drove into the mouth of a river?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a river?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Won't we run out of places to run if we keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've been completely trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy got behind us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking down on us from 5,000 meters back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that: A sunken ship. Fucking inauspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your asses and go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:04.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, you guys will come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll have to face me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, they've stopped by the sunken ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're not chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no point in even giving chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:52.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:04.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get excited when you wonder how they'll react in this crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They'll become a beehive before our superior weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't wait to see how they'll react.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:21.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they're boring and won't even try, then we'll just torture them to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no road ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to turn around and go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll be waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My gut tells me they set this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They want to finish this face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's going to ring the gong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:48.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you'll find them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient bastards who think they're gunmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the only choice left is to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well calm down, calm down, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call the police. That's better than dy-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:09.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're helpless. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's gonna get solved if you panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to survive use your head, your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, how about waiting for them to run out of fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:22.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The bastards are from E.O. They'll come to finish us before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:31.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a business paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check on my stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Kageyama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:45.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How's the damage to the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If even one round hits the torpedo we'll fly to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault for keeping it on the ship, you dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, I might have been able to use it for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste, but let's just throw it overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand something, now that I've thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:18.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:24.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you bother my thought process, I'm gonna let Revy nail you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a shoot out, face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At most we have an anti-tank rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They have rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like that chopper had heat-seeking homing missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. We're not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, what did you give him to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:55.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a head-on game of chicken right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:10:02.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This ship's speed and armaments, that sunken ship, they're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What you guys were just talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fly them to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:31.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By all accounts this ship is made to accelerate quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At full speed we're only this much into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, we don't have anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:43.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The plan won't work unless they're right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any guarantees, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:51.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're having a blast chasing us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Despite having a complete advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What reason would they have to restart the whole fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type to imagine himself as a gunman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:10.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we start a chicken race, he'll face us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:15.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any guarantees. From this point on, it's up to you as Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:22.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We sure picked up one crazy son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this is exciting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:32.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and being exciting is an important thing, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The radar, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take their challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:46.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:53.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they fire a rocket, fire the signal flare away from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see our dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:57.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a chicken race! Make them play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting! I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Use the flare gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:22.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the alpine course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you get in the cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:32.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They plan on using the sunken ship as a shield. Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:32.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When we cross paths we'll get them in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to end this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:40.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fuck you baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,300 feet left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,150.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,100!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fire #1! Fire #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I fucked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My head's not torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My sunglasses aren't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Amen, hallelujah, peanut butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lordy lord fucking Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never doing this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny? You ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the instruments are messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We need to fix them up. We're-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How about Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's out cold over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right before we hit, he howled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:15.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like a line by William Holden out of "The Wild Bunch".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:19.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And he looks so comfortable sprawled out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:32.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When that moment passed, the excitement from the adrenaline faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:37.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My boiling blood had gone back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Smart business is lovely, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:58.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, you look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're going to a Soho social.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:02.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Mr. Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:08.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We at Hotel Moscow have a code of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:13.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I thought you were the Burgenbiria Trade Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:17.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We followed through in our own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any grudges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:28.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The world is full of things that can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:33.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn to follow through in your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cover the details at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Okajima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima-kun? What are you doing? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Department Chief, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:00.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:10.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Fujiwara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:13.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:25.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:29.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for making you stay with those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:34.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, it'd be a waste to keep such a tough guy as a Japonski.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:38.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to us, if you ever need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He is no longer an employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A manager should no longer care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, why so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:07.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a hostage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:17.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know a place that could use a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're a delivery company...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and brush against the law from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's a boat that's blocking our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're blowing our horn but it's not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it couldn't be helped, to let that little bit leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We were prepared for that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Job well done, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Testing, testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:39.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning everyone aboard the St. Joan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:44.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wear the aloha shirt I got for you at the market?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because, we're on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:51.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This has become my job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:58.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone of the St. Joan, I apologize for the sudden request but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...please stop your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My personal opinion is that-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:16.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Complying with the request as quickly as possible, would be the best course of action!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, the St. Joan have opened up their communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We made contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And, what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:27.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we get out of their way, they will force their way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The time for being a gentlemen is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These moments make my prehistoric blood awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They have a rocket launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up limp-dicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My rockets are faster than electric signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:05.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to end up as a blood filled ghost ship, then stop, you shit-heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:17.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny-Boy, report to the Lun-i Pan that we've taken the St. Joan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:21.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and that they need to come get it before anyone starts a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:22.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:30.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh, John. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Takanori, how's it going,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,with your studies for college acceptance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:51.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About your daughter, she's been coming home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:55.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's only 18. Will you say something to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:10.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What color was the sea, when you went to the south on your business trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Color of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy was busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one may believe me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:25.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I became a pirate in the South Seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:29.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That huge ship was today's prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get back to port before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The China bowl at Tao Han...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...sells out fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're being targeted by pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:25.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the background on our client?
